enhanced_by.reason: The indexInfo method provides details about the index, which is necessary to validate the indexId parameter before redeeming the index plan.
The userIndexPlans method provides details about the user's index-linked plans, which can help ensure the plan is eligible for redemption.
The indexPlanRedeemHistory method provides the history of redemption transactions, which can be used to verify the success of the redemption operation.
The oneTimeTransactionStatus method checks the status of a one-time transaction, which can be used to verify the status of the redemption operation.
